In the High Court of Punjab and Haryana, Chandigarh. C.W.P. No.960 of 1997 Date of Decision: 12.12.2007 Paramjit Singh and Others

Petitioners Versus State of Punajb and Others.

Respondents CORAM: HON BLE MR.JUSTICE RAJESH BINDAL Present: Mr. K.G.Chaudhary, Advocate for the petitioners. Mr. Mr.Parveen Chander Goyal, Senior Deputy Advocate General, Punjab for the respondents. RAJESH BINDAL, J.

Learned counsel for the petitioner fairly states that the issue raised in the present petition is squarely covered by C.W.P. No. 18012 of 1997 (Rajinder Singh and Others v. State of Punjab and Others), which has been decided by judgment of this Court today. Accordingly, for the reasons stated in the aforementioned writ petition, the present writ petition is disposed of.

(Rajesh Bindal)

Judge December 12, 2007

DK
